 15/10/17 All fit men in camp sent to front line but 28 of us went on sick parad into Ypres . Away all morn saw the ruin of the place includ the Cloth Hall . After dinner issu with old rusti rifl put an afternoon clean them up . Went to bed about 6pm . 16/10/17 Were busi clean rifl readi for an inspect when Fritz start shell the camp . In 33rd btn 2 kill 2 wound in 35th ( our btn ) the pay Sergt was blown to piec . All men were order to scatter at 10.30am order came
